oad" data-width="808" data-height="554" data-src="https://cdn.wadiz.kr/ft/images/green001/2022/0531/20220531151210550_58.jpg/wadiz/format/jpg/quality/80/optimize" style="padding-bottom: 68.5644%;"></p><h3><u>성분, 배합, 함량, 맛, 디자인까지</u></h3><p>레놉티는 고객님들께 <strong>완벽한 이너뷰티 솔루션</strong>을 제공하기 위해 그 무엇과도 타협하지 않고 높은 퀄리티를 보장합니다.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img class="fr-fic fr-dib lazyload" data-width="798" data-height="1382" data-src="https://cdn.wadiz.kr/ft/images/green001/2022/0531/20220531174451497_86.gif" style="padding-bottom: 173.183%;"></p><p><img class="fr-fic fr-dib lazyload" data-width="808" data-height="1791" data-src="https://cdn.wadiz.kr/ft/images/green001/2022/0602/20220602160612976_8.jpg/wadiz/format/jpg/quality/80/optimize" style="padding-bottom: 221.658%;"></p><p><img class="fr-fic fr-dib lazyload" data-width="808" data-height="2828" data-src="https://cdn.wadiz.kr/ft/images/green001/2022/0608/20220608101134631_4.jpg/wadiz/format/jpg/quality/80/optimize" style="padding-bottom: 350%;"></p><p><img class="fr-fic fr-dib lazyload" data-width="808" data-height="1708" data-src="https://cdn.wadiz.kr/ft/images/green001/2022/0602/20220602160640433_29.jpg/wadiz/format/jpg/quality/80/optimize" style="padding-bottom: 211.386%;"></p><p><img class="fr-fic fr-dib lazyload" data-width="808" data-height="1572" data-src="https://cdn.wadiz.kr/ft/images/green001/2022/0531/20220531151508682_85.jpg/wadiz/format/jpg/quality/80/optimize" style="padding-bottom: 194.554%;"></p>', '/resources/images/p_certification.png', to_timestamp('2022.06.16 00:00:00', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), to_date('2022.07.10', 'RRRR-MM-DD'), to_date('2022.07.12', 'RRRR-MM-DD'), to_date('2022.07.14', 'RRRR-MM-DD'), 'Y', 0);

